p.s. totaly having a party during the break!"

column1: event,"yeah this week has been crazy. first off this whole going to college thing is crazy. uhhg how come i just cant be a bum in cali and lay on the beach all day. do you realize that would be totaly and i would absolutly love it. so yeah i have been looking at colleges and im taking the ACT in dec. 11. that should be fun. other than this week has been ok. wedensday...oh the election day. so happy that bush actually won! yeah all the liberals in our school were all mad and angry little kids. it was great. yes and what was a normal plan of picking up a mask that i left at jasons turns into steve and clint coming over and all of us nerds watching the election eating pizza. thats one wild party. anyways it was fun. well i am absolutly loving the cold weather we are having. i love the fall. plus it means it is one more step to thanksgiving and that means one more step to senior party! oh yes i am excited bc it is going to be the best nite ever. and let me say i will be taking plenty of pics and many of stories to tell. oh yes. also we are like 4 weeks away or something crazy to xmas which is totaly awesome bc thats my favorite holiday. today was good. i snuck in to kurios in which u are supposed to pay 3 bucks but i was sneeky enough to crawl through some people. haha it was great. i am doing awesome with this getting over someone. i think i should be like an oprah or something.
